receiving yard
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:an outer yard in a set of stock yards, where stock are first driven.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
