EGMONT A. AND P. SHOW GROUNDS.

The few improvements which were asked for at the annual meeting last year have not been given effect to. Where is the circular judging pen you speak of? Have the committee erected a race for the pig pens and a proper place for loading? Has the drinking trough in the receiving yard been shifted?
